public class Slf4jJdbcEventLogger
extends Object
implements JdbcEventLogger
A JdbcEventLogger built on top of slf4j-api logger.
Since:
3.1, 4.0 renamed from CommonsJdbcEventLogger to Slf4jJdbcEventLogger as part of migration to SLF4J
